Package: deltaccd
Type: Package
Title: Quantify clock gene co-expression relative to a reference
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: as.person('Jake Hughey <jakejhughey@gmail.com> [aut, cre]')
Description: deltaccd can infer progression of the circadian clock in
  transcriptome data in which samples are not labeled with time of day and
  coverage of the circadian cycle may be incomplete.
URL: https://github.com/hugheylab/deltaccd
